the reference. A single source may report statistics for multiple \"as of\" dates.\n|}\n\n==See also==\n{{Portal|Viruses}}\n* [[Health crisis]]\n\n==Notes==\n{{reflist|group=note}}\n\n== References ==\n{{Academic peer reviewed|Q=Q63740114}}\n{{reflist}}\n\n==Further reading==\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* Bullard, Stephan Gregory. 2018. A Day-by-Day Chronicle of the 2013-2016 Ebola Outbreak. Springer. \n*{{cite journal |display-authors=3|last1=Carroll|first1=Miles W.|last2=Matthews|first2=David A.|last3=Hiscox|first3=Julian A.|last4=Elmore|first4=Michael J.|last5=Pollakis|first5=Georgios|last6=Rambaut|first6=Andrew|last7=Hewson|first7=Roger|last8=Garc\u00eda-Dorival|first8=Isabel|last9=Bore|first9=Joseph Akoi|last10=Koundouno|first10=Raymond|last11=Abdellati|first11=Sa\u00efd|last12=Afrough|first12=Babak|last13=Aiyepada|first13=John|last14=Akhilomen|first14=Patience|last15=Asogun|first15=Danny|last16=Atkinson|first16=Barry|last17=Badusche|first17=Marlis|last18=Bah|first18=Amadou|last19=Bate|first19=Simon|last20=Baumann|first20=Jan|last21=Becker|first21=Dirk|last22=Becker-Ziaja|first22=Beate|last23=Bocquin|first23=Anne|last24=Borremans|first24=Benny|last25=Bosworth|first25=Andrew|last26=Boettcher|first26=Jan Peter|last27=Cannas|first27=Angela|last28=Carletti|first28=Fabrizio|last29=Castilletti|first29=Concetta|last30=Clark|first30=Simon|last31=Colavita|first31=Francesca|last32=Diederich|first32=Sandra|last33=Donatus|first33=Adomeh|last34=Duraffour|first34=Sophie|last35=Ehichioya|first35=Deborah|last36=Ellerbrok|first36=Heinz|last37=Fernandez-Garcia|first37=Maria Dolores|last38=Fizet|first38=Alexandra|last39=Fleischmann|first39=Erna|last40=Gryseels|first40=Sophie|last41=Hermelink|first41=Antje|last42=Hinzmann|first42=Julia|last43=Hopf-Guevara|first43=Ute|last44=Ighodalo|first44=Yemisi|last45=Jameson|first45=Lisa|last46=Kelterbaum|first46=Anne|last47=Kis|first47=Zoltan|last48=Kloth|first48=Stefan|last49=Kohl|first49=Claudia|last50=Korva|first50=Mi\u0161a|last51=Kra